    <div class="gem-c-title
  
  gem-c-title--margin-bottom-5">
    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      Promotional material
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU Settlement Scheme: employer toolkit
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    The employer toolkit equips employers with the right tools and information to support EU citizens and their families to apply to the EU Settlement Scheme.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="column-two-thirds metadata-column">
